UML:TaggedValue.value: A entity imported from ISO 19115, including: - Fees -Planned availability date and time - Ordering instructions -Turnaround
A service type name from a registry of services. For, example, OGC may be the name space and catalogue may be the identifier.

Provides for searching based on the version of serviceType. For example, we may only be interested in OGC Catalogue V1.1 Services. By maintaining version as a separate attribute, users can easily search for all services of a type regardless of the version.
